com.autopia4j.framework.core

  • Packages that use com.autopia4j.framework.core 
    Package Description
    com.autopia4j.framework.core
    Core library of the autopia4j framework
    This library can be used in conjunction with any Java based automation tool
    com.autopia4j.framework.reporting
    Reporting library of the autopia4j framework
    This library can be used in conjunction with any Java based automation tool
    com.autopia4j.framework.reporting.impl
    Reporting library implementations (currently HTML and Excel) of the autopia4j framework
    These implementations can be used in conjunction with any Java based automation tool
